    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fallen Depths</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A roguelike action horror game where you explore procedurally generated maps and aim to reach the top floor. Use logical strategies to overcome grotesque monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various items can be found within each floor. Gather weapons and bandages to prepare for battles on higher floors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332000/extras/76014e7a6c54b4c8c354978beaf57749.poster.avif?t=1734134493\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332000/extras/76014e7a6c54b4c8c354978beaf57749.webm?t=1734134493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332000/extras/76014e7a6c54b4c8c354978beaf57749.mp4?t=1734134493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat with Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may encounter monsters roaming the floors, leading to combat. Explore the floors while either preparing for or avoiding battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332000/extras/41e3f85b46e065e886367be5d7b554d9.poster.avif?t=1734134493\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332000/extras/41e3f85b46e065e886367be5d7b554d9.webm?t=1734134493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332000/extras/41e3f85b46e065e886367be5d7b554d9.mp4?t=1734134493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock skills as you clear stages and use them to take on even more challenging stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Streaming Guidelines</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We allow gameplay streaming and video creation of this game, regardless of whether you are an individual or a corporation, and regardless of whether it generates revenue.</p>",
